OL,3,CTrump says 'no time frame' for war end
OL,4,Cas Lebanon and Israel set to meet
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump has said
OL,7,Fthere is "no time frame" for ending
OL,8,Fthe conflict in Iran, after a
OL,9,Fceasefire between the two nations was
OL,10,Findefinitely extended.
OL,12,FPakistan had planned to host a second
OL,13,Fround of talks on Wednesday, but the
OL,14,FWhite House suspended Vice President
OL,15,FJD Vance's planned trip to Islamabad
OL,16,Fas Iran rebuffed efforts to restart
OL,17,Fnegotiations.
