OL,3,CTrump says 'no time frame' for war end
OL,4,Cas Lebanon and Israel set to meet
OL,6,FIran acknowledged the ceasefire
OL,7,Fextension but there was no
OL,8,Fconfirmation of when a new round of
OL,9,Ftalks would begin, according to state
OL,10,Ftelevision.
