OL,3,CTrump says 'no time frame' for war end
OL,4,Cas Lebanon and Israel set to meet
OL,6,FTrump told Fox News on Wednesday there
OL,7,Fwas "no time pressure" surrounding the
OL,8,Fceasefire with Iran and "no time
OL,9,Fframe" for ending the war, denying
OL,10,Fclaims he wanted to "get it over"
OL,11,Fbefore the US midterm elections.
OL,13,FMultiple Iranian news agencies
OL,14,Freported that the paramilitary
OL,15,FRevolutionary Guard had attacked a
OL,16,Fthird ship in the Strait of Hormuz on
OL,17,FWednesday, throwing into question
OL,18,Fefforts to end the war.
