OL,3,CTrump says 'no time frame' for war end
OL,4,Cas Lebanon and Israel set to meet
OL,6,FThe attack was reported to have been
OL,7,Fon a vessel called the Euphoria, which
OL,8,Fwas described as being stranded on the
OL,9,FIranian coast.
OL,11,FThe United Kingdom Maritime Trade
OL,12,FOperations centre (UKMTO) had
OL,13,Fconfirmed two other attacks in the 24
OL,14,Fhours previous.
OL,16,FPanama's foreign ministry wrote in a
OL,17,Fstatement that a ship flying under its
OL,18,Fflag, owned by Italian company MSC
OL,19,FFrancesca, had been "forcibly taken"
OL,20,Finto Iranian waters on Wednesday.
