OL,3,CTrump says 'no time frame' for war end
OL,4,Cas Lebanon and Israel set to meet
OL,6,FThe nation accused Iran of violating
OL,7,Finternational law, and said the
OL,8,Fseizure represented a "serious attack
OL,9,Fon maritime security and constitutes
OL,10,Fan unnecessary escalation".
OL,12,FOfficials from the US Department of
OL,13,FDefence have said it will take months
OL,14,Fto clear mines in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,15,Fonce the war is over, AP reports.
OL,17,FIsrael and Lebanon talks continue
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
