OL,3,CTrump says 'no time frame' for war end
OL,4,Cas Lebanon and Israel set to meet
OL,6,FIsraeli and Lebanese officials will
OL,7,Fmeet in Washington on Thursday to
OL,8,Fdiscuss extending the ten-day
OL,9,Fceasefire that went into effect last
OL,10,FFriday.
OL,12,FA Lebanese journalist was killed
OL,13,FWednesday during an Israeli airstrike
OL,14,Fon a house in southern Lebanon where
OL,15,Fshe had taken cover, causing Prime
OL,16,FMinister Nawaf Salam to accuse the
OL,17,Fnation of war crimes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
