OL,3,CTrump says 'no time frame' for war end
OL,4,Cas Lebanon and Israel set to meet
OL,6,FAmal Khalil, who had been covering the
OL,7,Fconflict in Lebanon for the daily Al-
OL,8,FAkhbar newspaper, had sought shelter
OL,9,Fin the home in al-Tiri after an
OL,10,Finitial strike hit a vehicle in front
OL,11,Fof her. A freelance photographer was
OL,12,Falso injured.
OL,14,F"Targeting journalists, obstructing
OL,15,Faccess to them by relief teams, and
OL,16,Feven targeting their locations again
OL,17,Fafter these teams arrive constitutes
OL,18,Fdescribed war crimes," Salam said
OL,19,Fearly Thursday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
